<h2 style="color: #003155;"><strong>Enjoy a January short break from just £249 per person!</strong></h2>
<p>Our 4/5 nights short breaks are perfect if time is precious or maybe you’re hoping to sneak in an extra week of skiing next season.</p>
<p>What are you waiting for – you deserve to get back on those slopes and we can’t think of a better place to spend your first week of 2022?</p>
<p>Start as you mean to go on in 2022 – book your January short break from just £249pp.</p>
<p style="color: #003155;"><strong>Check out our best deals below – sale ends Tuesday 19th October.</strong></p>
